(6, 'Selamat Datang Ke E-AUDIT', '', 'Slider', '2016-01-04', 'Off', '[{"name":"files\\/mais-building_n6wl8esa.jpg","usrName":"mais-building.jpg","size":56754,"type":"image\\/jpeg","thumbnail":"files\\/thmais-building_ibve7wkp.jpg","thumbnail_type":"image\\/jpeg","thumbnail_size":22275,"searchStr":"mais-building.jpg,!:sStrEnd"}]'),
(7, 'THE OPENING OF WORLD ULAMA CONFERENCE', '<span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">Alhamdullillah, All Praise be for Allah, by whose grace and blessings we are gathered here today to discuss matters regarding our religion, Islam and the ummah. I would like to thank the organisers for giving me this opportunity to officiate this conference and to speak on a matter that is close to our hearts.</span><br style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><br style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">2. But before that I would like to welcome all participants and guests, especially those from outside Malaysia to this country, this multi-racial and multi- religious country where everyone accepts the constitution which provides that Islam is the official religion but the practice of other religions by their followers are guaranteed. We believe in religious harmony as advocated by Islam in Surah Al-Kafirun, ayat five and six. " Nor will ye worship that which I worship. To you your Way, and to me mine."</span><br style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><br style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">3. Islam does not have a system of hierarchical priests but the Muslim scholars, the learned ones or the ulamas as they are generally referred to, play an extremely important role in the life of Muslim individuals and the Muslim community. Such is their influence that the stability and progress of Muslim countries depend much on them.</span><br style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><br style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">4. The ulamas are said to be the successors or the "warasah" of the Prophet. This makes them even more powerful. Their words are often taken as the religious truth and seldom does anyone dispute any pronouncement made by them.</span>', 'Berita', '2016-01-04', 'On', NULL),
(8, NULL, 'Laman Sistem E-audit sedang dalam proses selenggaraan. Harap Maklum', 'Pengumuman', '2016-01-12', 'On', NULL),
(10, '"BAHAGIAN AUDIT DALAM, MAIS MENERIMA KUNJUNGAN AUDIT 5S DARI MPC"', '6 Jan 2016 (Rabu) - Bahagian Audit Dalam, MAIS telah menerima kunjungan audit 5s dari pihak MPC. Bahagian ini telah terlibat sebagai salah satu Zon 5s di MAIS dan dikenali dengan Zon Prof. Dr. Hamka. <br><br>Skop Auditan 5s oleh pihak MPC melihat bukan sahaja dari aspek kekemasan, susun atur dan kecerian lokasi zon. Malahan pihak MPC lebih menekankan aspek penambahbaikan hasil dari Amalan Persekitaran Bersih 5s yang diwujudkan di setiap Zon.<br><br>Sepanjang program auditan yang dijalankan oleh pihak MPC di Zon Prof. Dr. Hamka, auditor MPC amat berpuas hati dengan pengamalan persekitaran 5s di Zon ini. Sesi ini telah disambut oleh seluruh pegawai di Bahagian Audit Dalam, MAIS yang diketuai oleh Ketua Audit Dalam, MAIS, Pn. Kasmawati Abdul Latif.<br>', 'Berita', '2016-01-13', 'On', '[{"name":"files\\/AlCLcQq6NfNJYSUbDHZ9m_xlQAb4ZjTe3YPpa04h_7pi_6csp8alg.jpg","usrName":"AlCLcQq6NfNJYSUbDHZ9m_xlQAb4ZjTe3YPpa04h_7pi.jpg","size":70268,"type":"image\\/jpeg","thumbnail":"files\\/thAlCLcQq6NfNJYSUbDHZ9m_xlQAb4ZjTe3YPpa04h_7pi_ako8trg0.jpg","thumbnail_type":"image\\/jpeg","thumbnail_size":13165,"searchStr":"AlCLcQq6NfNJYSUbDHZ9m_xlQAb4ZjTe3YPpa04h_7pi.jpg,!Amlz0HkCmlxMPpdPu9Pnj7_Qr_m9_NGznloRn8yRBQPA.jpg,!:sStrEnd"},{"name":"files\\/Amlz0HkCmlxMPpdPu9Pnj7_Qr_m9_NGznloRn8yRBQPA_12epj3xh.jpg","usrName":"Amlz0HkCmlxMPpdPu9Pnj7_Qr_m9_NGznloRn8yRBQPA.jpg","size":53089,"type":"image\\/jpeg","thumbnail":"files\\/thAmlz0HkCmlxMPpdPu9Pnj7_Qr_m9_NGznloRn8yRBQPA_hkbuuq34.jpg","thumbnail_type":"image\\/jpeg","thumbnail_size":11108}]'),
